data.description: Welcome to living easy in this bright and airy townhouse in the Steeplechase community, conveniently located just over a mile to the downtown Littleton light rail station and shops! This space lives large with vaulted ceilings, skylights, and lots of light. Sip your morning coffee in front of your cozy gas fireplace on chilly Autumn mornings, and enjoy the mountain views from your private balcony in the Summer months. Your main level is equipped with a large bedroom with South facing windows allowing abundant natural light. The loft serves as a den, flex space, or is easily converted to a 2nd bedroom. The mountain views from this space & the balcony will not disappoint! Never worry about parking again with your attached garage, and additional reserved surface level parking spot. With your outdoor community pool, laundry in unit, easy access to public transportation, HWY 85, Aspen Grove shopping center, Downtown Littleton bars, shops & restaurants, light rail, Littleton Golf and Tennis Club, and endless parks and trails, this townhome has it all!
